name: Anatolian Eagle Flight Academy
about: Anatolian Eagle Flight Academy is a professional aviation training institution founded by Cenk Ozer, an experienced aviation professional with a rich background in flying. Located in the United States, the academy is a small, family-owned business with a deep passion for aviation. With thousands of hours of flight experience, our instructors specialize in training pilots for various aircraft, including general aviation and commercial models like the B-737, B-757, and B-767. We offer comprehensive flight training programs tailored to meet the needs of aspiring pilots, ensuring they receive the highest quality instruction to achieve their aviation goals. Our commitment to safety, excellence, and personalized training makes us a trusted choice for those seeking to embark on a career in aviation. We are dedicated to turning your aviation dreams into reality.
